These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, dahlia, orchid, tulip
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, bus, ship
 1. the person driving the bike is the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 8. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
 9. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Flower   | dahlia | poppy    | tulip   | orchid    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Transport     | bike       | airplane | ship  | bus      |

