 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is the farmhouse house##1
10. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

