 1. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
 2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Food          | lime    | radish        | potato     | banana          |
| City           | berlin | boston        | edinburgh | marseilles |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

