.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, journalist, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, thriller, zombie
There 4 different types of food: orange, papaya, spinach, onion
 1. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the architect##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the doctor is between the journalist and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the journalist is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
10. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating onion##1
11. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person eating onion is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Job           | musician   | architect  | doctor        | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | zombie     | thriller      | disaster   |
| Food     | papaya | spinach | onion          | orange     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish, mouse
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the owner of the mouse is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
 7. the social-worker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Pet   | mouse      | goldfish    | ferret        | chinchilla |

 